These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, cranberry
1. the person eating onion is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Food   | cranberry | onion |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
House: colonial, farmhouse
1. the farmhouse house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| House   | colonial | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
